values: Can I just say that I hate my family right now and that my dad makes me so angry. He's talking about not letting me go to Central. Which really pisses me off because Greensboro is NOT where I want to be at all. It NEVER has been. And I could be with all of the credits I deserve and took and happy in my place if my parents hadn't harassed me to leave Hartford and told me they wouldn't pay for my schooling. Now he wants me to not go to Central because "he cant afford it." I didn't ask him to fucking go to Ghana for two months knowing he wouldn't get paid. And if he had fucking been paying my credit card THAT HE HAS BEEN USING then I would be able to take out a fucking loan to cover the difference of my finacial aid. But he has not been paying my credit card and has FUCKED UP my credit. I got the credit card and left it at home so that I wouldn't use it and this man maxed it out and didn't bother to pay for it. WHAT THE FUCK IS HIS PROBLEM!!! So he's fucked up my credit and left up to him I'll be unhappy and angry living miserably in this god forsaken piece of shit southern fucking shithole town called Raleigh like him. And that makes me angry because Terance GOT TO CHOOSE where he wanted to go to school and also got to stay where he started. I don't GIVE A SHIT if it is in-state. Because we were living in MA when he got in. And the ONLY reason I said I didin't care if we moved to this POS place is because they kept harassing me AT THE WORST times when I was fucking depressed asking me if we could move. Not only was I sick of them bothering me but I was ready to say anything to get them the hell out of my face. And I've experienced VERY FEW good things in this place AND I HATE IT. I want to be elsewhere. Where I can be happy and make friends who aren't fake who GET me and stay there and be stable and have stable relationships. But I didn't get to choose where I went to school, because my first choice school was in Canada. He told me I can't leave the country. I didn't get into my next choice school. And the school that I finally chose to go to, a school that I liked, a school I had friends at, a school I did well in, a school WHERE I LEARNED SOMETHING I was forced out of because of my asshole dad. And forced to go to that PIECE OF SHIT SCHOOL which will probably be the reason I don't get into medical school. This is just ridiculous. WHY THE HELL CAN'T I GO WHERE THE FUCK I WANT TO GO, HUH!?!?!? I wish I could say this shit to my dad because there's some other bullshit I would like to bitch at him about, but I won't say it here because someone might hack their way into my online diary and read it when they have no business reading it and then go and tell my brother that I "Have stuff about my life on the internet" Even though it is NO BUSINESS OF ANYONE'S WHAT THE HELL I PUT ON THE INTERNET!

Can You Feel It I know why I'm mad... I'm mad at him for making me do it, because I had just like 10 minutes before had the conversation with him about how I didn't want to have sex with him and why that is. So yea, after having that conversation with him I am mad at him for that much. Also, as bad as this sounds and as much as I hate to admit it; I actually kind of liked it. Granted, if it didn't take place the way it did it would've been better... But I don't like that it was like 'enjoyable'. So I'm mad at myself for that, because I didn't want to like it, then I could've been mad about that too, that he like wasn't 'gentle' or something...but he was... kind of... excluding the times I tried to get up and he pulled be back. He didn't like hit me or pick me up and toss me (which has happened as hard as that is to believe). Even so, I'm still mad at him for it; I'm glad he didn't like hurt me physically but that kind of thing hurts on the inside and will in my case manifest itself into physical pain because that's how things are for me... anyways... I walked away for like an hour and now I don't know what I really wanted to say other than that I'm mad for two reasons... done

You Were Just As Broken As Me What is wrong with me that I manage to get myself into shitty situations??? It's gotta be me, cuz this is not the first time some bullshit like this has happened with me and sex and someone I don't want to do it with... I liked Dante until last night. Not liked a lot; but I liked him enough to want to get to know him. I'm really just mad at myself, I guess cuz I wonder if I can actually hold it against him for wanting to hook up with me when he was drunk as hell and I had made out with him at my apartment before we went to the party... But I was curious and kisses don't really mean that I have to have sex with someone. I don't know why I'm mad. I mean, I know I have reason to be mad; I just haven't had enough time to think about it to really figure out why I'm mad, because I feel inclined to blame myself for this one- that maybe I sent him mixed signals or something. But I wasn't like shaking my ass in his face or anything. He had been to my apartment he's seen my room he saw Theo's toothbrush in my toothbrush holder; he said "Aww look at you and your boyfriend's toothbrush sittin there," HE SAID THAT!!! Granted, Theo isn't my boyfriend, but he saw the toothbrush and he jumped to the conclusion that I had a boyfriend and I didn't say anything to make him believe different (but I did do differently... the kisses) Maybe I'm mad at myself for not following him in my own car to that party last night- not that I was sober enough to drive at 6am this morning- SO I would've had to take a cab back anyway. But the walk to Walgreens to meet the cab that I called did bring new meaning to the phrase "walk of shame" for me; that is while morning traffic was just picking up I felt like I was being stared at; oh wait, I was being stared at, cuz there was no side walk so I was walking on the side of the road looking like a prostitute or a runaway highschool kid or something... I don't know exactly what I looked at but I know I looked bad, 'specially since I had cried all my makeup off.yyyeaaaa..... I made Lauren feel bad about not coming to get me. I didn't mean to. I just didn't think to take a cab until I had walked a good 1/2 mile in my heals and saw Bluebird cab drive by... heh... I texted her like 19 times while I was still there, and I called her and she didnt answer and i called her house phone to wake her up even though I couldn't speak to her. I just needed her to wake up and read my texts. All of the text messages I sent her reached her phone around 8:15 when I was sitting in my living room nursing my feet, which walked over a mile in heals that aren't that comfortable when I'm sitting down let alone walking up a ridiculously sized mountain- ok... medium sized hill- either way, i was wearing the wrong shoes for this walk. "Date rape" that was the first thing Theo said after I told him the story. Then he grabbed my butt and he was like "it's getting bigger... that's why all the guys want you." And he asked me why I didn't call the cops and I was like "because I've been to jail and I don't want to go again." And he was like "it was self defense." But it was also self-defense last year when I hit Emily after she hit me in the face... Alright, it wasn't self-defense last year; that... that was pride. But it could've been considered self-defense. Either way I would've had to go to jail this morning and call my mom and tell her that she was gonna have to find at least 1000 bucks to get me out of jail. I say that cuz that's how much my bail was in Hartford. And Theo of all people should know that cops always and will always and forever make everything worse in any situation. Theo was like "what does he look like?" and I was like "skinny, black, big lips lol." And he's like "he got money?" and I was like "I guess... he works at a bank america" and hes like "i'm a beat dat mutha fuckas ass and rob 'em" lol... I think maybe he deserves the ass whoopin (I did say "no"). 'specially since I told him about my 'incident' with the marine last year... Ex-airmen, Dante had to do the same...Not exactly the same cuz I can definitely say that I did not send that guy mixed signals, but I can't say that I didn't with Dante. Either way, he's a Fuckin' jerk... Matt texted me to ask me "how life is treating [me]" lol I don't know, but I think he may have noticed my away messahge which stated "it's just me and my feet... no one is ever there when I actually need them." I told him "awful." He requested twice for me to talk to him about it and I was like "nothin's wrong" he asked me if I was lying and I said "yes." and he was like "So talk to me" and I was like "I don't want to talk about it." and he left his open invite for me to call him and talk to him (like usual)... *smiles* that Matt... He's a sweetheart. Anyway.... I'm gonna go to Lindell's little Shin dig at his new apartment... can't get raped by a gay guy... well, I could lol, but I don't think its likely...

They open up your heads, they're fuckin with your mind What can I say? I'm smiling when I'm with him I can't help but to frown when I'm without him Today a knock came at my door And I actually jumped knowing it was him... In my dreams... I know he's with other women But I think I know where his heart is I know I can't have him fully Yet I'm so happy Yet I feel good with him And like I'm not alone Because he's there Until we part ways again And I'm alone And all I can think about is his well-being Is he ok? Does he need me? Does he care the way I do? Maybe it's me Maybe I care too much Maybe the wanting hasn't left me Not like it should have All I want is for him to be here And all I wish is for the knocking to be him Instead of my imagination So my anxiety and this anticipation can retreat So that maybe I can sleep in peace - 1:42am

Rise the Wake and Carry Me with All of My Regrets I don't see what the problem is... Why doesn't god just take me now and get it over with???? All my money is gone.... WHERE IT WENT is a Fucking MYSTER to me, but whatever its gone. And I'm supposed to go see Dima in DE tomorrow... How does one do that with no money??? Oh, I'm the fuckin' retard who is going to make that happen. And for what?!?!?! So that I can see him and be happy for one more moment in time before I have to force myself to leave his side again. And choke back tears for 8 hours as I drive back here alone and heart broken. I don't know what my motive is. I really, honestly and truly don't know anymore why I bother or why I care or why I bother to care to give my heart to anybody ever I talked to Kate the other day about whether I should go to see Dima and how I want to be over him so that maybe I can finally start to enjoy the company of other guys. She told me that she's still not over Terance and it's been 4 years! I don't want to pine over Dima for 4 years, nor do I want to be with anybody but him right now. Even though I am basically stringing along two guys right now. Well, really just one... cuz let's be honest Theo wouldn't care if he found out about Jeremy... So I ask myself again, why am I going to DE to see Dima? Partially because I'm sick of sitting around in Greensboro and so I can say I did something over spring break. And I guess I have this stupid naive idea that maybe, just maybe if I go up there to see him that I'll finally be able to convince him to move down here to be with me. But why bother? When I know the chance is so slim its invisible... Maybe because I know I'll hate myself if I let the opportunity to see him and look into his eyes and see how much he cares about me and if its worth my tears every night pass... because I know if I can't say that I tried and did everything I could to get him to come down here to be with me, then I wasted my time with him when I was in Hartford. I don't want to be able to say that. Shower

When you come back we have to make new love I hate to bad mouth my sisters, but one of them annoys THE HELL out of me when she drinks :-( I'm talkin' like I don't want to even speak to her anymore when she's drunk.

I need to get rid of my selfishness... It keeps me from growing as a person. yea... that and i don't want to like reggie, but i think i do a little or something and that bothers me. That I'm not in control of myself. I want control. I want control over myself and my life and my feelings and I don't have it and I don't like it.

Bye bye beautiful 
Don't bother to write

Face step, let down.

This is not a small cut that scabs and dries and flakes and heals... Would you be my little cut... Love is not like anything especially a fucking knife... I have the worst headache and I was wondering why and then I remembered it's cuz I cried earlier. Why did I cry earlier??? Because Dima's ring fell off my finger at Shelly's house and broke in half and as it did so my heart did the same. Yes, I cried over Dima's broken ring. He gave it to me and I said I'd never take it off and it broke IN HALF. I could like kill myself I feel so alone... I'm a failure. I can't even keep a ring on my hand how sad is that. I called him as soon as it happened... He was out somewhere. There was lots of noise in the background. He was like "It's all good." but its NOT. It is to him but it's not to me because it actually means something to me, because he gave it to me. He put the ring down on my lap and said it was made out of stone and I looked at it and said "r u giving this to me?" and he looked at me and said "u want it?" and I nodded and smiled the way I only do with him and put it on my thumb and he said "u can keep it." and he gave me matching lil stone too... and i broke the ring because I'm a failure who can't do anything right :-( That ring is only the beginning... a sign that my life shall further crumble that I- no matter how hard I try to fight am a slave to that which I hate most about myself- my emotions; I'll always be a hopeless ball of emotions deprioritizing only to prioritize again, letting go only to grab hold again and running forward only to look back and watch the past suck me in. I am alone. That is the truth, that no matter how many people are in my company I'm only me and alone. I can't hide from that nor can I run from it. I can only accept it. And eventually give in. I CANT BELEIVE I BROKE HIS FUCKING RING!!!! I'm so upset. I'm a slave to a ♥ that won't let go

And When It's All Done I wrote a song. I think about Dima way too much... Here's my song: Last Night I had a dream My world came crashing down upon me And all I could do was watch And feel the tears fall down my face I looked up to the sky And asked God please take this pain away from me And all I could think is how he's given up on me It was then I knew that it would never end Chorus: I once had my life together I once had all my priorities straight I once knew what I wanted Now all that has changed And now all that I want He's what I want That man I cannot have Last night I had a dream I asked you if you were with her When you answered these visions came over me It's been 6 months and I still can't believe Maybe we'll still get together And thoughts of that spot in your bed That used to belong to me Chorus: I once had my life together I once had all my priorities straight I once knew what I wanted Now all that has changed And now all I want He's what I want That man I cannot have Last night I had a dream My world can crashing down upon me And when I woke I looked around And realized it was not a dream

You take it all away but never give it back I just realized a minute it ago that I'm still not over Dima... and that I never fully got over Richard. I can't read my poem about Richard without starting to cry and I can't think about how happy I was with Dima without crying or at least starting to. It's sad really... My favorite picture of me and Dima together is the first one we ever took together on our second date to... I forgot the guy's name but he's a weird redhead... well it was to his b-day party... We went out to breakfast with him and some other guys on one of my last days in CT. And we listened to his band play... Well, Dima listened and I fell asleep on the couch because I was kind of bored. But even being bored I was just happy that I was there with him... point: Every time I look at that picture I start crying, so I put a different picture in my frame and hid that one on the backside of the pic I put in. That way, it's still framed but I don't have to look at it and think about how I went through Bradley airport with red eyes and in histerics crying over leaving my boyfriend, whom I just knew I'd never see again. Granted, I saw him again but he wasn't my boyfriend anymore and I knew it was going to happen. I knew it all along and tried to prepare myself, but I couldn't. I don't think I'd get back together with Richard... I say this because of how I am and how I've called him 8 times in the past 2 weeks and he has answered only once and the one time he answered i dont think he meant to cuz he hung up on me lol... He says he's excited for me to come up and I believe him; he's just so weird about like socializing even if it's with me, which is bad. Dima says he's not comin' down here now. I thought he was :::::::: Shrugs :::::::: I wonder how life would've been if I lost my v-card to Dima. At least I'd have a happier relationship to remember. I was happy knowing I was with Richard, but he disappointed me on many occasions so it wasn't very happy... I remember the time I cheated on him, because he cancelled a date on me by not calling me or answering my calls... so basically he stood me up. He said he was working and that his phone died... Which I believed. It was just the fact that he didn't call me. I remembered I pushed my parents to go out that night to a jazz club so that I could have sex and go wherever he wanted to take me without having to explain anything to my parents. Yea, that didn't work out... I was so mad at him that I called Josh K. who left a party, came and hooked up with me and then left. It didn't make me feel as good as I thought it was going to lol Yea... I hate being home alone because I start thinking about the past and getting all sad and crying... I don't know if I'm friends with Jessica any more... She called me last night to apologize for saying some shit to me, but I was still asleep when I was on the phone so I don't know what she said to me really... She was like "I'm not apologizing for what I said, I'm apologizing for how I said it." and I kind of just grunted "uh-huh." So she said she'd let me go. That was at like 9pm... I've been up since then its 9:12am now... I guess I should stop avoiding her and have the conversation that we should have had back in October when I got mad at her in the first place... I guess I can call her now, since my day has already been ruined by my previous thoughts. Those thoughts will rule my day as they have so often done in the past at random times. Jen's pissed at me because I said some rude shit to her about Jon... I didn't mean to say it the way that I did. I actually didn't mean it the way that it came out. Well maybe I did a little... No... No I didn't mean it that way at all... I felt bad about it and I apologized to her like 2 1/2 minutes after I said it after she put up an away message saying "this is the line don't cross it" o0ops... Anyways... I'm gonna do something else...

This is Fact not Fiction
I haven't been thinking very much lately. I'm just bored really. Finals came around and I shut my brain off before I could get myself organized. I don't like UNCG. At Hartford it was like finals gradually came after Thanksgiving, but here it's like I came back from thanksgiving and the next Monday I was taking finals... actually it wasn't like that, it's what actually happened. Oh well, what can ya do right? I have an F in bio, a D in Cognitive psych which means I have to take it over even though I was going to anyway because I didn't learn shit from the guy, I got a C in Film and a B in Clinical Psych yay me... I'm going to be a super senior. Now I have to replan my next five years. This shit sucks. Next semest, I have to bring my GPA up. Which won't be hard, I just have to focus. When I'm focused like I was last year I am unstoppable. It's ridiculous how well I did last year. I got 100s on essays. No one gets perfect scores on essays, but I did. And I did a few without the help of James. I've spoken to him like 3 times this semester. Med school will keep you busy... I miss him. eh... Anyway, I just felt like doing something... But I don't really have anything more to say...

The Trolly Wood is taking me away I want a boyfriend... I'm tired of being alone and sexless... I'm sick of seeing other people excited about their relationships and not having one of my own to be excited about... I've exhausted the thought of me ending up alone forever, without children, without a family, without a person to share my dreams with... and that is my only complaint about my life now. I think I've become too focused on the future, but I feel like I'm too old not to be. Granted, last year I had this conversation with Tewauna that I'm young and I want to have fun and that I wanted a boyfriend but that I wasn't going to start considering marriage right away because I had just turned 18 and had and have yet to be in a relationship for longer than 6 months... 3 months really... Because let's talk about it: Richard and I started in i think like March or april and I'm more inclined to say april even though I vaguely remember snow being on the ground the morning I went into school and told Lia about my first time, but anyway... yea we'll call it March... I didn't see him again until August the night before I was moving away and he only came then to say goodbye and every date we made between those dates was cancelled by him because he was working or something or blah blah blah... maybe that's y he says I will take much to get what I want... yea i def. wouldn't put up with that now, and every guy I meet for the rest of my life can thank him for that... After him there was Doug C. who died, which isnt very chill but yea he and i were at the like 3 week point or something... Then there was Will who shouldn't really count because it wasn't a real relationship but for 4 months I had a title... I may have seen him once or twice a month for that 4 month period if I was lucky... oh yea and when I did see him he was all about the sex; lucky for him he was so much about the sex enough that I'd purposely try to annoy him by declining... so yea then there was Mike 2 weeks... then mike again like a week and a half and then julian like 5 months 'cept like we were together a week before i left for college and I hooked up with other guys so it really doesn't count... then mike again which is this time around and I'm just not gonna bother breaking up with him again cuz he just doesnt get it. Then Dima... first real like actual relationship from the end of February till July so like 5 months, 'cept like almost 2 of those months I was here. So that's like 3 months. aaaaaannnndd my point was....: oh yea... I was in no place last year to be all about getting married and having kids right away like she is, but I do worry about my time passing and never finding the right person until it's too late to have kids and stuff. And before Dima I hadn't been in a real, healthy relationship where I felt comfortable enough to open up and say what's on my mind and stuff.. I mean kind of with Julian but our relationship by no means was healthy, because he begged me to go out with him. And the only reason I accepted was because he said that I could cheat on him if I wanted to as he was begging and he probably regretted that later. But anyways... 4 relationships with titles in the last 4 years and at this point I'm sick of waiting around; I'm sick of wasting my time with worthless guys; I'm sick of thinking that maybe my worst nightmare is going to come true as God's way of further smiting me. but yea... that's my complaint. My only wish is to succeed and to have someone to share my successes with.

Passing through Unconscious states Hate to be a lil' emo bitch, but this whole Matt dating a Chi Omega shit is really bothering me. Why? I dunno... I can be honest I don't know him that well, but a crush is a crush and I can't help it. I actually wouldn't have any kind of a problem with him dating a sorority girl if she were an AKA or a Delt or a Zeta or whatever, but a Chi O-fuckin-mega... It's kind of a slap in the face cuz if I'm not mistaken he and I had a long ass conversation about why I didn't join a black sorority, yet he goes out to date a girl in a white one... hmmm... And we could say that I'm jealous, but I had already gotten over the fact that he wanted to "keep it friendly." It just bothers me of his choice, a "chi-o girl." Not to mention, he's on her facebook pic from when they went to the Crimson and Creme dance or whatever... Which I actually wanted to go to... kind of... ok so I didn't want to go, but I would have gone if I had been asked... And the other day was her birthday and the fact that the facebook friend pics rotate shes on the front page of my profile today... I just can't stop seeing her. And I saw her yesterday when I was goin to luminaries with Teresa. I fuckin' walked right by her and if I had known at the time what I found out later last night I wouldn't have smiled at her. In fact, I probably would have given her the worst look in THE WORLD. So I guess it's better that I didn't know at the time. And ok I never liked Chi Omega... so I never really had a real significant reason to dislike the Chi Omegas; o0o0o0o0o but now I do. Ok and it's not like she purposely was like my friend and knew I liked him and went and started dating him plus I'm not the kind of bitch who'd go cause problems in a relationships because I'm jealous or whatever because I 1) have way to much pride to do that 2) don't really want him anymore 3) I have way to much pride to do that cuz he doesn't like me. But it's not him not liking me that bothers me and its not him having a girlfriend that bothers me cuz he told me he was talkin' to someone its the fact that of all the girls on this campus of all the friggin sorority girls it HAD to be a FUCKING CHI OMEGA. Its the fact that she's a chi omega that bothers me. If she had been an AD pi I'd probably feel the same. With all the white sororities I'd feel the same unless it was one of my sisters. I should have set him up with one of my sisters when he asked me to

Candy Shop Ok. I'm pissed again lol... This stupid bitch on poets.com got mad at me for actually scrutinizing her poem and giving her advice when SHE ASKED ME FOR HELP, because she thought I offended her. I send her a message back and I was like "i actually spent time trying to help you because you asked me and I could have just said "the flow is off," but to me a review like that is not helpful." Like she got mad and said that I basically told her that she's a bad writer and to be honest her poem was SHITTY there were A LOT of errors. And one of her reviews actually did say "the flow is off and some places." THATS IT. I like to point out to people where the flow is off if i think so, otherwise you're wasting your time and theirs because obviously they didnt think the flow was wrong when they posted it. But this particular woman actually sent me an e-mail before saying "iom trying to make edits to this poem will u review it blah blah blah." And I thought wow she actually wants a real review out of me; no, she just wanted me to say "it's fine." And she had the nerve to call me ignorant. IM SORRY but when I get reviews that say "your flow is off" I don't bother to go back and look at my poem 1) because I don't have issues with flow so if someone says that to me I'd know they were saying it because I said it to them 2)if the flow is off I'm not going to notice where you think it's off because I WROTE IT that's the point of the site (to encourage new writers to write and to help them get better). I'm sorry but you don't get better at ANYTHING with "thats good." You get better with constructive criticism and if you cant take that criticism then you don't need to put your poetry on a site like poets.com. You need to put it in your livejournal or xanga so that your friends can tell you it's good because they don't want to hurt your feelings. And this other person not sure if its male or female but ill say male. HE got mad at because he attempted to write a limerick and did the syllables and rythmn wrong; so in my review, I told him that the syllables and rythmn are off and pointed out where they are off and WHY they are wrong. He had the nerve to tell me there are no rules on syllables in a limerick and that if there is a rule to show him the site. So... And I know he's gonna get mad about this... I went on google read the first 5 sites and copy and pasted the link of each one in the e-mail saying "proof: 1) link 2) link 3) link 4) link 5) link Thank you for your time." I'd get mad if someone proved me wrong like that, but anyways... lol I was just a lil annoyed that people can't take criticsm. Yes, my poetry is very important to me and it speaks of A LOT of my feelings, but I can take criticsm on it if it deals with structure of it or like the diction. There's a difference if you come to me and say "your poem sucks because its about love." THATS when you get offended; THATS when you get mad, but "maybe you should change the words in line 4 of stanza 5 because it throws the flow off maybe you can try this 'blah blah blah'" THAT IS HELPFUL and i don't understand why that woman got so mad about it. Granted; I had atleast one something to say about at least one something in every stanza, BUT it wasn't I who said that the poem was bad it was she. And if I made her feel that it was bad ok sorry, but you asked me to review it to help you which means you need to be able to put your feelings that are in the words aside and take the criticism for what the poem actually is not what its about. I didn't say anything about what the poem is about. When you ask someone to review your poem to help you then you need to be able to take it because it will make you and your poem better.

Lookin back in November I talked to Josh K. online today. It was a pretty long conversation for us recently. He tried to convince me to move to Vegas with him. I was like 'ur retarded if u think i'm gonna follow u around the united states.' It was amusing though we talked about a bunch of junk... School, love... about that love shit though, I realize that it has never really been about me not liking me. Well, not recently. I love myself. I like myself the way I am and if other people don't oh well. But I've been so much better about seeing the good and people and not disliking people I've barely exchanged two words with. I just feel empty right now. Yes, the grades upset me but they aren't the reason I feel the way I do. And as much as I'd like to say its not cuz I don't have a guy; it is. And I can't say that I'm unhappy with my life. I like it. My life is fine and I am happy... for everyone else and all the exciting things that are happening for them. And I'm sorry if I sound selfish... but what the fuck about me?!? I gotta say I've been patient. I've waited for something so exciting as to change the dynamic of my so very disgustingly boring life and it has yet to come along and sweep me off of my feet. I gotta say this year more bad things have happened to me than good... In less than a year I've managed to get my first speeding ticket, become witness to he corrupt institution that is our Safety net (the police), run out of money, transfer into an awful school, GAIN 15 FUCKING POUNDS (wanna kill myself... not really), get all of the stuff I bought when I went shopping stolen ON MY BIRTHDAY, get a boyfriend and be forced to 'mutually' break up with him. And all the good stuff that has happened was with him. I don't know why I'm really so bothered by it though. That's the story of my life right?? The matchmaker who cannot find her own that will last; the quiet girl who is too busy judging the world while trying to make the best of it; the girl people love to her face and hate when shes not looking; the lady all the guys could see themselves in bed with but not together with. That's me. No, the world's not out to get me; God's testing me. I wish He wouldn't. Anyway. It's still light outside... thats a first write an entry at 5:30 in the evening. Semi-formal is tonite. I'm not going... I was going to. I was never really excited about it though, but I asked Matt Flamer to go with me and he said he'd check the date cuz there was a concert he wanted to go to...Kanye West. And it is tonight. He's part of the reason I decided not to go cuz i didnt wanna go alone... But also cuz... ok so he was my only reason for not going. I told him that I like him the other day. Haven't really spoken to him since. Needless to say; I don't think he feels the same way lol... Which I'm fine with, but I'd still like to be able to talk to him. I saw Theo walking down the street yesterday when I was driving to campus from my job at the church nursery. I just immediately got sad. I knew it was him before I even passed. That walk and his head. I thought "Is that Theo?" and it was. I don't know why it makes me sad to even think about him... I don't know. I actually liked him i guess. I could supress that for a while, but I guess I just need to admit that I liked him. And I let him go for Jessica whom I never even talk to anymore cuz I'm mad at her for making me make that decision. I'd NEVER do that to her. NEVER. I mean she said shit about him being a bumb and using me for a place to stay... And ok fine I'll admit; no, he didn't have a place to live... But he wasn't staying on the street before he met me, so he obvisouly had somewhere to stay whether it was his own place or not. That didn't bother me. No, he doesn't have his own car, but I had stopped driving him everywhere after like the first 2 weeks of seeing him. I liked him. And I guess I still do, but it's like, with him, everything was so much more real. Like this is the world and I can sink or swim and as weird as it sounds I liked that. I liked being with him and knowing whether he said so or not that I was his girl and he was my guy. Even though it wasn't official. I know that he knew I wouldn't talk to him anymore if he did stuff with another girl. And for that whole two months when we were together I didn't want to find a guy to be with. I was satisfied with where I was with him. I could go to the club and I could go to parties without him and come back and get in the bed with him and feel good when he held me. And vice versa. When he went to clubs and shit and came back to get in my bed with me I felt like I could trust him and that he hadn't been with another girl and then came here to hop in my bed and go to sleep partially cuz we usually ended up doing something when he got back anyway but still... Being with him made me feel good and real. Like I'm not living in someone elses dream cuz something good finally happened to me. I felt like he needed me; not for a place to lay his head, or a vagina to stick his cock into, or anything like that. Just like I was the evaporated milk to his tea or the sugar to his kool aid. I don't really feel like I had to get him out of my life. I just wanted him not 'living with me.' But I think I might have gotten him fired from his job :-( I miss him. It's been like a month now. Exactly a month actually. Anyway i'm gonna lay down for a couple hours til I go hang out with Terance.
